name: Lookup IP addresses stored in Microsoft 365 Excel using IP2Proxy
description: Make will watch for new rows in a specified Microsoft 365 Excel worksheet at regular intervals and lookup IP addresses in IP2Proxy, then update a row in Excel using information found. The template uses this [example worksheet](https://1drv.ms/x/s!AnDK8KmbvjyFkFJ49QJmcrRWZWhZ?e=50ed0j).
